ht be damaged.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Timer with Automatic Stop</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Turns off the active zone once the set time elapses.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Booster Function</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Allows you to focus all the power of the induction cooktop (hob) in the preset zone, to speed up the boiling and cooking times.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Slide Controls</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">This handy \\u201ctouch control\\u201d system makes it possible, for example, to increase or decrease the operating temperature by sliding your finger from right to left or vice versa.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Child Safety</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Once this function has been set and until it is disabled, the induction cooktop (hob) does not turn on by turning on the controls.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Overheating and Liquid Spill Protection</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">If the cooktop (hob) overheats or liquid spills occur, a safety device trips and stops operation.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Limited 2 Year Parts and Labor Warranty</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories